The stress contributions comprise the viscous stress ${\boldsymbol{{\Pi}}}^{viscous} = 2 \eta{\boldsymbol{{E}}}$, where $\eta$ is the viscosity,
the elastic stresses ${\boldsymbol{{\Pi}}}^{elastic}=-P{\boldsymbol{{I}}} -2\lambda q_{}{\boldsymbol{{H}}}+ {\boldsymbol{{Q}}}\cdot{\boldsymbol{{H}}} - {\boldsymbol{{H}}}\cdot{\boldsymbol{{Q}}}-{\boldsymbol{{\nabla}}} {\boldsymbol{{Q}}} \frac{\delta \mathcal{F}}{\delta {\boldsymbol{{\nabla}}} {\boldsymbol{{Q}}}}$,





